BEGIN_PGML On a cold snowy day, the temperature in your home is a cozy [`[$initial]\,^{\circ}F\text{,}`] but then you lose power and heating. Your home temperature begins to drop at a rate of [`[$rate]\,\frac{^{\circ}F}{\text{hour}}\text{.}`] How long will it take before your home is [`[$final]\,^{\circ}F\text{?}`]
[_]{$time}{20}
END_PGML
